{"tid":832470,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知由幾時開始 我已經對自己失望 對世界絕望","createTime":"2018-09-22T18:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T09:21:53.000Z","uid":207219,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9f40783c2675647ab21ef12f0fe2b41fd48bfe","tid":832470,"uid":207219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:13:37.000Z","msg":"周不時會覺得好唔開心<br />\n覺得自己好冇用 失去曬方向<br />\n一時唔小心控制唔到情緒就好易將負能量發洩喺其他人身上<br />\n有時仲要係心愛嘅人上<br />\n之後會好內疚 更加覺得自己好差<br />\n好易諗起過去傷心嘅回憶 其實好需要被愛 好需要人嘅關心<br />\n但因為受傷太多 偏偏起咗一層保護網 有時都唔想講咁多"},{"pid":"1d81b9fc643942467f82f550f63d1a23ae0e35db","tid":832470,"uid":207219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:19:45.000Z","msg":"只想由得我嘅諗法靜靜喺角落磨滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516e26784f1a9d65f75d6ed424155b425fc80ddd","tid":832470,"uid":75297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:40:07.000Z","msg":"周圍嘅人睇自己好似好平常<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a9108302ac0b853943b697f6c951ed97e74b58","tid":832470,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/23/023013_fee4e47f3e4c529b1f2c751035a4492c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F023013_fee4e47f3e4c529b1f2c751035a4492c.gif&h=e0417305&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"917e96f722f8701acb3c86840b31ae7c91247162","tid":832470,"uid":184808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:43:05.000Z","msg":"有時候係條街聽住歌都會嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26ff3b782d17b97f5302ca8ac0fba08dd789991","tid":832470,"uid":207219,"like":0,"dislike"